28/06/2010
TIRANA, Albania -- Interior Minister Lulzim Basha announced on Saturday (June 26th) that Albania will give property seized from drug traffickers to families with a drug victim at home. 
Marking International Day Against Drugs, Basha said that Albania's front against drugs involves all institutions. 
There are about 30,000 drug users in Albania, including 10,000 using heroin. 
(Top Channel, News 24, Ora News - 26/06/10)
